Class FileZipOriginal

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileZipOriginal

  • public class FileZipOriginal
extends java.lang.Object
    This command line tool takes two arguments 1. The Root of the Windchill folder. e.g: "Z:/Windchill" (exactly as shown. NO forward slash (/) after "Windchill") 2. a date, in this format yymmdd. e.g: 121130 (November 30th, 2012)

    asaif
